Ladies and Gentlemen, as of tonight, the <a href="http://pub106.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showMessage?topicID=791.topic">Ragefire Rotation list</a> is now retired, permenantly. (more)<br>As of right now, there is no harm whatsoever to any cleric if every cleric pursues their epic, except possibly Rauntek, and he is nearly done himself. The epic drops are uncommon, and the rage-spawning npc repops a half hour after poofing. The need for any list for this spawn no longer exists.

Congratulations to all that received their epic through the list over the last year and a half without bitterness or anger amongst guilds, and good luck to all clerics to follow us, your camp is now much more enjoyable than ours had been. 

